{
  "title": "Creamy Dutch Tiger Prawn Curry",
  "description": "A nutty and tender monsoon Dutch dish featuring tiger prawns, this halal-friendly curry is made with a mortar-pestle-pound spice blend. It is a delicious and flavorful meal perfect for dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
